<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Legal Disclosures | Clearline Capital</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Legal Disclosures for the Clearline Capital public website." />
  <style>

    :root { --black:#050505; --ink:#f7f2e8; --muted:rgba(247,242,232,.68); --soft:rgba(247,242,232,.42); --line:rgba(218,174,98,.28); --gold:#d6a85e; --gold2:#f0d6a0; --serif:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif; --sans:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif; }
    * { box-sizing:border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
    body { margin:0; background:linear-gradient(180deg,#050505,#080705 48%,#050505); color:var(--ink); font-family:var(--sans); overflow-x:hidden; }
    body:before { content:''; position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:0; opacity:.08; background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.45) .5px,transparent .5px); background-size:3px 3px; mix-blend-mode:overlay; }
    a { color:inherit; }
    .site-nav { position:sticky; top:0; z-index:5; min-height:86px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:20px; padding:16px clamp(20px,4vw,54px); background:rgba(5,5,5,.94); border-bottom:1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.09); }
    .logo img { width:118px; height:auto; display:block; }
    .back-link { color:var(--gold2); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.18em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.55); padding-bottom:5px; }
    main { position:relative; z-index:1; padding:clamp(64px,8vw,108px) clamp(22px,5vw,72px); }
    .legal-shell { max-width:1040px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; grid-template-columns:minmax(190px,260px) minmax(0,1fr); gap:clamp(34px,6vw,86px); align-items:start; }
    .legal-kicker { color:var(--gold2); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.30em; font-size:12px; margin-bottom:18px; }
    h1,h2 { font-family:var(--serif); font-weight:400; margin:0; text-wrap:pretty; }
    h1 { font-size:clamp(42px,6vw,76px); line-height:.98; letter-spacing:-.045em; }
    .meta { margin-top:24px; color:var(--soft); font-size:12px; line-height:1.65; letter-spacing:.06em; text-transform:uppercase; }
    .side-nav { position:sticky; top:118px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); padding-top:18px; display:grid; gap:12px; }
    .side-nav a { color:rgba(247,242,232,.62); text-decoration:none; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.15em; text-transform:uppercase; line-height:1.45; }
    .side-nav a:hover { color:var(--gold2); }
    .legal-body { border-top:1px solid rgba(214,168,94,.34); padding-top:8px; }
    .legal-body section { padding:34px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.09); }
    .legal-body h2 { color:var(--gold2); font-size:clamp(24px,2.7vw,34px); line-height:1.08; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin-bottom:18px; scroll-margin-top:126px; }
    .legal-body p, .legal-body li { color:rgba(247,242,232,.72); font-size:15px; line-height:1.78; }
    .legal-body p { margin:0 0 14px; }
    .legal-body ul { margin:0 0 14px; padding-left:20px; }
    footer { position:relative; z-index:1; padding:38px clamp(22px,5vw,72px); border-top:1px solid rgba(247,242,232,.1); color:rgba(247,242,232,.62); }
    footer .wrap { max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; gap:18px; }
    .footer-disclaimer { max-width:980px; font-size:12px; line-height:1.65; color:rgba(247,242,232,.58); }
    .footer-links { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px 20px; }
    .footer-links a { color:var(--gold2); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none; }
    @media (max-width:760px) { .site-nav { min-height:72px; } main { padding-top:54px; } .legal-shell { grid-template-columns:1fr; } .side-nav { position:static; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; } h1 { font-size:clamp(38px,11vw,52px); } .legal-body p, .legal-body li { font-size:14px; line-height:1.7; } }
    @media (max-width:430px) { .side-nav { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Legal navigation">
    <a class="logo" href="/" aria-label="Clearline Capital home"><img src="/logo-champagne-132.webp" srcset="/logo-champagne-132.webp 132w, /logo-champagne-264.webp 264w" sizes="118px" width="132" height="83" alt="Clearline Capital" /></a>
    <a class="back-link" href="/">Return to site</a>
  </nav>
  <main>
    <div class="legal-shell">
      <aside aria-label="Page sections">
        <div class="legal-kicker">Clearline Capital</div>
        <h1>Legal Disclosures</h1>
        <div class="meta">Effective date: 2026-07-22<br />Policy version: CLC-LEGAL-DISCLOSURES-2026-07-22-v1</div>
        <nav class="side-nav">
          <a href="#about-clearline-capital-llc">About Clearline Capital LLC</a>
          <a href="#informational-website-only">Informational website only</a>
          <a href="#no-securities-or-fund-interest-offer">No securities or fund-interest offer</a>
          <a href="#no-professional-advice-or-fiduciary-relationship">No professional advice or fiduciary relationship</a>
          <a href="#access-requests-and-invitation-codes">Access requests and invitation codes</a>
          <a href="#opportunity-submissions">Opportunity submissions</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </aside>
      <article class="legal-body">
        <section>
              <h2 id="about-clearline-capital-llc">About Clearline Capital LLC</h2>
              <p>Clearline Capital LLC is a Wyoming limited liability company organized on December 19, 2025. Clearline Capital LLC evaluates business opportunities nationally and uses this website to provide general information about its business focus and access process.</p>
              <p>Legal mailing address:</p>
              <p>Clearline Capital LLC 30 N Gould St Ste N Sheridan, WY 82801 United States</p>
              <p>Email: info@clearlinecapital.co</p>
              <p>The mailing address above is a legal mailing address. It should not be understood as a representation that Clearline Capital LLC maintains an operating office at that location.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="informational-website-only">Informational website only</h2>
              <p>This website is provided for general informational purposes only. It is not intended to provide investment, legal, tax, accounting, valuation, financing, brokerage, or other professional advice. Visitors should consult their own advisors before making business, financial, legal, tax, accounting, or investment decisions.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="no-securities-or-fund-interest-offer">No securities or fund-interest offer</h2>
              <p>Nothing on this website is an offer to sell, or a solicitation of an offer to buy, securities or interests in any investment vehicle or fund. Clearline Capital LLC does not use this public website to publish offering terms, accept investment commitments, accept investor funds, or promise investment returns or performance.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="no-professional-advice-or-fiduciary-relationship">No professional advice or fiduciary relationship</h2>
              <p>Use of this website, submission of information, or receipt of a response from Clearline Capital LLC does not create an advisory, fiduciary, legal, tax, accounting, brokerage, agency, partnership, joint venture, employment, or confidential relationship.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="access-requests-and-invitation-codes">Access requests and invitation codes</h2>
              <p>Invitation codes are used solely to route access requests and introductions.</p>
              <p>Submitting an Access request does not create any commitment, approval, right to participate, right to compensation, exclusivity, confidentiality obligation, or obligation for Clearline Capital LLC to review, respond, proceed, finance, acquire, partner, or enter into any transaction.</p>
              <p>Receipt, possession, entry, or validation of an invitation code does not mean that a person is accredited, qualified, approved, invited to invest, admitted to a transaction process, or eligible to participate in any offering.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="opportunity-submissions">Opportunity submissions</h2>
              <p>Please do not submit confidential, proprietary, regulated, or sensitive personal information unless a separate written confidentiality agreement is in place. If you submit an opportunity, introduction, referral, company information, or related material through this website, you grant Clearline Capital LLC permission to review and evaluate the submission for its internal business purposes.</p>
              <p>No referral fee, finder fee, brokerage fee, success fee, advisory fee, carried interest, equity right, reimbursement right, or other compensation is created merely by submitting an opportunity, referral, introduction, or related information through the public website. Any compensation, fee, reimbursement, equity right, carried interest, exclusivity, or similar arrangement must be set out in a separate written agreement signed by Clearline Capital LLC.</p>
              </section>
            <section>
              <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>
              <p>General, legal, and privacy inquiries may be sent to info@clearlinecapital.co.</p>
              <p>Acquisition opportunities, referrals, and introductions should be submitted through the Access form rather than by email.</p>
            </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="footer-disclaimer">Clearline Capital LLC is a private investment and acquisition firm. This website is for informational purposes only. Nothing on this website is an offer to sell, or a solicitation of an offer to buy, securities or interests in any investment vehicle or fund. Submissions do not create a confidential relationship, transaction commitment, exclusivity, compensation right, or obligation for Clearline Capital to respond or proceed. Please review our Legal Disclosures, Privacy Policy, Terms of Use, and Submission Terms.</p>
      <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="Legal links">
          <a href="/legal-disclosures">Legal Disclosures</a>
          <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>
          <a href="/submission-terms">Submission Terms</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
